-- Common Table Expression
WITH fts_contains_vu_cte1 AS (
    SELECT *
    FROM fts_contains_vu_t
    WHERE CONTAINS(txt, 'resveratrol or (grape and wine)')
)
SELECT * FROM fts_contains_vu_cte1
GO
~~START~~
int#!#text
985#!#<p> It 's thought that the chemical resveratrol , found in red grapes and red wine , is the reason why 
986#!#Resveratrol , a chemical found in red grapes and red wine , may protect against hearing loss
988#!#In a study conducted at the Henry Ford Hospital in Detroit , healthy rats were less likely to suffer noise-induced hearing loss when given resveratrol before being exposed to loud noise for a long period of time 
992#!#Study leader Dr Michael Seidman said : ' Our latest study focuses on resveratrol and its effect on the body 's response to injury - something that is believed to be the cause of many health problems including Alzheimer 's disease , cancer , ageing and hearing loss 
993#!#Resveratrol appeared to reduce the damage to hearing from loud noises
994#!#' Resveratrol is a very powerful chemical that seems to protect against the body @ @ @ @ @ @ @ @ @ @ cognition brain function and hearing loss 
997#!#The study found that resveratrol reduced noise-induced hearing loss in rats exposed to potentially deafening sounds 
998#!#Dr Seidman said : ' We 've shown that by giving animals resveratrol , we can reduce the amount of hearing and cognitive decline 
1004#!#resveratrol 	drugs<newline>cause	loud	noises
1008#!#grape 	wine<newline>drinkers
~~END~~


